        Creates a JMS message listener definition based on a MessageListener implementing class.
        Parameters:
        name - the listener name
        connectionName - the connection name that this listener is attached to.
        session - the JMS session
        destination - the JMS destination
        selector - the message selector
        messageListener - the MessageListener instance
        poller - an optional MessagePoller to retrieve messages via receive().
